<font color="yellow">Hee Ja membunuhnya, 'kan?</font>

955
01:03:36,570 --> 01:03:38,630
<font color="yellow">Hei! Yeong Won!</font>

956
01:03:39,570 --> 01:03:41,770
<font color="yellow">Kasar sekali.</font>

957
01:03:43,630 --> 01:03:46,290
<font color="yellow">Hei, jangan makan lagi.</font>

958
01:03:46,290 --> 01:03:47,700
<font color="yellow">Tak bisa jadi artis nanti.</font>

959
01:03:48,600 --> 01:03:50,660
<font color="yellow">Kau harus menggoyangkannya lebih asik.</font>

960
01:03:50,660 --> 01:03:54,360
<font color="yellow">Ya begitu. Berputar.</font>

