977
01:05:11,490 --> 01:05:13,900
<font color="yellow">Kita ajak ibumu jalan-jalan.</font>

978
01:05:15,870 --> 01:05:17,490
<font color="yellow">Oke, ayo.</font>

979
01:05:17,490 --> 01:05:20,260
<font color="yellow">Akan kuracuni suamiku dan
