980
01:05:20,260 --> 01:05:22,260
<font color="yellow">Lalu kita keliling dunia.</font>

981
01:05:22,260 --> 01:05:24,390
<font color="yellow">Jangan bicara begitu.</font>

982
01:05:24,390 --> 01:05:25,800
