986
01:05:48,900 --> 01:05:51,800
<font color="yellow"><i>Aku merindukan suaramu</i></font>

987
01:05:52,270 --> 01:05:54,230
<font color="yellow">Oh, Maria.</font>

988
01:05:54,770 --> 01:05:56,000
<font color="yellow">Ibu.</font>

989
01:05:56,430 --> 01:05:57,870
<font color="yellow">Tebak dimana kami.</font>

990
01:05:58,300 --> 01:06:00,070
<font color="yellow">Kami di persimpangan Hyeoncheon.</font>

991
01:06:00,400 --> 01:06:02,250
<font color="yellow">Anakmu ini hebat, 'kan?</font>

