<font color="yellow"><i>Janji kita</i></font>

997
01:06:15,600 --> 01:06:17,830
<font color="yellow"><i>Tidak ada artinya</i></font>

998
01:06:18,540 --> 01:06:22,730
<font color="yellow"><i>Kita lepaskan bersama angin</i></font>

999
01:06:23,170 --> 01:06:25,070
<font color="yellow">Hati-hati.</font>

1000
01:06:28,270 --> 01:06:31,770
<font color="yellow">Sam Deuk, telepon anakmu
untuk menjemputmu!</font>

1001
01:06:32,370 --> 01:06:36,420
<font color="yellow"><i>Jika saja kau peduli padaku</i></font>

1002
01:06:36,420 --> 01:06:39,460
<font color="yellow"><i>Malam ini salju turun pertama kali</i></font>

1003
